The paper focuses on multilingual multimodal representation learning, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a method for generating synthetic data, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper involves the evaluation of image-sentence retrieval performance, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves the use of models and algorithms, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
